title: Eagles, Patriots, Lakers, World Series, & where Colin was right and wrong
itunes:title: Eagles, Patriots, Lakers, World Series, & where Colin was right and wrong
description:
Colin discusses the problems with the Philadelphia Eagles, why the New England Patriots continue to win, why the World Series will be great, the brawl between the Los Angeles Lakers and the Houston Rockets, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, James Harrison, and Caron Butler.
